Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:35.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\N趙荘の命令は直ちに前線に伝わった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:38.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本陣を動かすか…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.68,0:21:39.05,Kingdom-Main,Wan,0,0,0,,Moving the headquarters, huh?
